snippet.title: Hyper DBZ - TENSHINHAN RELEASED!
snippet.description:
http://network.mugenguild.com/balthazar/char_tien.html  download.

All your patience is rewarded with the release of Tenshinhan/Tien!
A special thank-you to all our testers and all of you who contributed sprites for the kicking intro (as featured in this video).

-Tien sprites by Balthazar.
-Tien coding by AlexSin.
-Tien voice by Mike Varker, Chiaotzu voice by AlphaProto.
-Background music is 'Mysterious Master'  by DaMarcus008.
-VS and Victory jingles by DaMarcus008.

Be sure to redownload Gotenks as well - he was slightly updated to work properly with TenShinhan.
http://network.mugenguild.com/balthazar/char_gotenks.html download.
How-to-add video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c1YvNtg06ps

Online Movelist (includes full credits) - http://network.mugenguild.com/justnopoint/HDBZ/movelist/
Balthazar's Hyper DBZ page - http://network.mugenguild.com/balthazar/index.html
Hyper DBZ Discord invite - https://discord.gg/fgWjRtY
Hyper DBZ Mugen Fighters Guild - http://mugenguild.com/forum/hyper-dbz.412
